article.description: Prairie View 106, SW Assemblies of God 61
article.headline: Prairie View 106, SW Assemblies of God 61
article.linkText: Prairie View 106, SW Assemblies of God 61
article.story: PRAIRIE VIEW, Texas -- Alex Richman came off the bench to score 24 points, all on 3-pointers, to help lead Prairie View to a 106-61 victory over Southwest Assemblies of God on Tuesday night. Darnell Hugee added 23 points and had 15 rebounds for the Panthers (2-4). He hit all nine of his field goals. Christopher Jones added 17 for the Panthers and Tim Meadows scored 12. Chris Valliere scored 14 points for the Southwest Assemblies of God (4-1). Prairie View led 54-35 at the half.
